metadata.name: Zen
metadata.description:
Original art by Sepimnft, 4500*5000 , 14 mb , jpg file .
Life is about balance, Be kind , but don’t let people abuse you. Trust, but don’t be deceived.Be content, but never stop improving yourself. (Zig Ziglar),

Zen : a Japanese sect of Mahayana Buddhism that aims at enlightenment by direct intuition through meditation ,along with an emphasis on self control & insight 
 Zen has 9 symbols, that I used 2 Symbols of that in my art : Enso & Yin Yang , 
Enso : means a mutual circle r circle of togetherness, Enso can be a elegant state which can also accept imperfection as perfect and the spirit of harmonious cooperation.
Yin Yang :This symbol represents harmony & peace in motion, which is the central concept of zen
